{"tid":957824,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[童年] 等左九年 馬神彈終於番黎啦","createTime":"2018-12-27T10:15:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T13:59:30.000Z","uid":129551,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"fe9fd3f04afa2ef053e76875e457b913160fa99c","tid":957824,"uid":129551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:15:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  九年前，當小弟仲係中學雞嘅時候<br />\n一番到屋企就會開三色台嘅放學ICU黎睇<br />\n試過有一排 勁沉迷打BS 覺得紅色頭髮個主角好L型<br />\n就係Brave嘅最後一集...<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">馬神彈死L左aaaaaaaaar</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n細個嘅我完全接受唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放棄咗BS <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過就係琴日 我見到有人話佢會番黎 仲比左條link我睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2jIArahTqi8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2jIArahTqi8&d=FVM6g6NACJYo7aJBQQ6zKJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=79ad5a36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2jIArahTqi8</a> <br />\n<br />\n哇屌!!!!! 睇完仲開心過魯魯修復活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同各位巴打分享我男神幾L型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mJ2Kzzy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmJ2Kzzy.png&h=ae5454a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a8b65bee82a28365f7335b020d1ab3c5df6b19f","tid":957824,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:16:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e860f2a3ba61201506f8b3480a77fa8119b1ded8","tid":957824,"uid":224452,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-